     <text:p text:style-name="P177"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-3"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Dou_note#cite_ref-3" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T26"></text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T21"></text:span><text:span text:style-name="T10">Adagiu latinesc scolstic, cu nelesul literal: a jura n adevrul celor spuse de magistru (ca naintea unei afirmri sacrosancte)</text:span></text:p>
